---
// FactsSection component - Statistics and data about Gen-Z recruitment
---

<!-- Facts & Figures Section -->
<section
  class="h-svh bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-purple-200 flex items-center justify-center px-16"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-6xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-6">
        Facts & Figures
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-purple-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Gen-Z recruitment is evolving rapidly. Here's what the data tells
        us about reaching the next generation of talent.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Statistic 1 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 text-center"
      >
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-4">72%</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
          Mobile-First
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          of Gen-Z job seekers use mobile devices as their primary job
          search tool
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Statistic 2 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 text-center"
      >
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">3.2s</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
          Attention Span
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          average time Gen-Z spends on a job posting before deciding to
          apply
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Statistic 3 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 text-center"
      >
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-4">89%</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
          Social Proof
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          want to see company culture and employee testimonials before
          applying
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Statistic 4 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 text-center"
      >
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">45%</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
          Video Content
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          prefer video job descriptions over traditional text-based
          postings
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"
    >
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-6">
          Why Traditional Recruitment Fails
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-purple-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-500 text-xl">✗</span>
            <span
              >Lengthy application processes lose 67% of candidates</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-500 text-xl">✗</span>
            <span
              >Generic job descriptions don't resonate with Gen-Z values</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-500 text-xl">✗</span>
            <span
              >Lack of transparency about company culture and growth
              opportunities</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-6">
          Our Approach Works
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-purple-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-500 text-xl">✓</span>
            <span>3x higher application completion rates</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-500 text-xl">✓</span>
            <span
              >Authentic storytelling that showcases real company culture</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-500 text-xl">✓</span>
            <span
              >Interactive content that engages and informs simultaneously</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
